<h4>Dan</h4>
<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/b8edf0a426265fcce4e820f1f30ca4aa?s=32&amp;d=monsterid&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' />Software developer, Bitcoin "hater", friend of BitcoinNotBombs. || @orblivion Twitter and Identi.ca || https://joindiaspora.com/u/ill_logic</div>
<footer class="post-footer postdata fix">
		<span class="tags tax"><span class="icon">&nbsp;</span>Tagged with: <a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/tag/bubble/" rel="tag">bubble</a>, <a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/tag/dr-bob-murphy/" rel="tag">Dr. Bob Murphy</a>, <a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/tag/gold/" rel="tag">gold</a>, <a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/tag/gold-vs-bitcoin/" rel="tag">gold vs. bitcoin</a>, <a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/tag/greater-fool-speculation/" rel="tag">Greater Fool speculation</a></span>
