  <!--widget start --><aside id="suf-featured-posts-2" class="suf-flat-widget widget-suf-featured-posts"><h3>FEATURED ARTICLE</h3><div id="suf-featured-posts-2-fc" class="featured-content index-hidden  pager-numbers fix">	<div id="suf-featured-posts-2-slider" class="slider fix clear" style='max-height: 250;'>		<ul id="suf-featured-posts-2-sliderContent" class="sliderContent fix clear" style='max-height: 250;'><li class="sliderImage sliderimage-top  " style='height: 250; '><a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/beginners-guide-to-off-the-record-messaging/"   class=''><img src="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/wp-content/uploads/thumb-cache/OTR-280419b639c2d427e0ea0724297fe72e-1x1-6-nocrop.png" alt="Beginners&#039; Guide To Off-the-Record Messaging" class="featured-excerpt-top"/></a><div class="top"  style=' background: #eaeaea; color: #424242; ' ><p><ins><a href="http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/beginners-guide-to-off-the-record-messaging/" class='featured-content-title' style='color: #424242;'>Beginners&#8217; Guide To Off-the-Record Messaging</a></ins></p><p>This is a sequel to my earlier post Beginners&#8217; Guide to PGP which was the first in a series of posts aimed at introducing new bitcoiners to various encryption technologies. In this post we&#8217;re going to teach you how to <a href='http://www.bitcoinnotbombs.com/beginners-guide-to-off-the-record-messaging/' class='excerpt-more'>[...]</a></p>
